{"tid":801224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【免費午餐？】國米想曾想免費簽莫迪歷 佩雷斯嘲大想頭","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T16:33:11.000Z","uid":57237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4a23d00c887a29258ca8878603516172ec13fc","tid":801224,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"剛獲得歐洲足協年度最佳球員的皇馬中場莫迪歷，被視為當今球壇較出色的全能中場之一，他早前曾經與國際米蘭扯上關係，但皇馬會長佩雷斯一直拒絕放人，他日前更透露，原來對方想不費一分一毫就簽入這位皇馬「 10 號」。<br />\n佩雷斯向傳媒透露，國際米蘭希望能免費簽入這位在世界盃上表現出色的全能中場，他直指對方「大想頭」，又表示生平從來沒有遇過有人想不花錢就買入他們的 10 號皇牌。<br />\n另外，莫迪歷這次以 313 分贏得歐洲足協最佳球員，拋離排第二名的 C 朗拿度 90 分，這亦是 2014 年以來，首次不是由 C 朗拿度或美斯贏得這個獎項。"},{"pid":"2dd412cfb4deec61976cb9d769aea85f0a00f2a4","tid":801224,"uid":197857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"係真既話都幾弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e232825292a6d245f8a60ca5713687e806731","tid":801224,"uid":37827,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:59:13.000Z","msg":"原來乞衣米蘭唔係淨係講緊ac米蘭"},{"pid":"cc83579bd61a5f5e73ab3c13efa44133ac623aaf","tid":801224,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"占士免費送都肯"},{"pid":"ffb91a5b8f50d0030c377c55c9b3aa0b6d712423","tid":801224,"uid":19556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"想免費簽世界最佳中場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e1b186df326e7caa628638bb173d7c0bbb3561","tid":801224,"uid":99960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"以前叫米蘭雙雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家叫米蘭雙乞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b4ecee2a2db196543a485e22d6405b087251a0","tid":801224,"uid":31914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16